	Ta có
	\begin{eqnarray*}
		x(t)&=&x_1(t)+x_2(t)=2\cos\left(\dfrac{\pi}{3}t+\dfrac{\pi}{6}\right)+2\cos\left(\dfrac{\pi}{3}t-\dfrac{\pi}{3}\right)\\
		&=&2\cdot 2\cos\left(\dfrac{\pi}{3}t-\dfrac{\pi}{12}\right)\cdot\cos\dfrac{\pi}{4}=2\sqrt{2}\cos\left(\dfrac{\pi}{3}t-\dfrac{\pi}{12}\right).
	\end{eqnarray*}
	Vậy pha ban đầu bằng $-\dfrac{\pi}{12}\approx-0{,}3$.
	}

