	Như vậy, ta được $$ \heva{&G_1G_2\parallel MN, G_2G_3\parallel NL\\&MN, NL\subset(BCD)\\&G_1G_2,G_2G_3\subset(G_1G_2G_3)}\Rightarrow (G_1G_2G_3)\parallel (BCD) .$$
